{"tid":1411703,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有料爆!!!!!馬鞍山撚同我入黎!!!!!!!","createTime":"2019-08-05T04:21:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T06:51:04.000Z","uid":238378,"like":514,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":69,"replies":[{"pid":"a329e95aee6c6bc4c29aa7a5d3e0acbdf095c219","tid":1411703,"uid":238378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T04:21:19.000Z","msg":"見到近幾日大家都去包圍馬鞍山警署 想講講隔離個停車場<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FOcVuuD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFOcVuuD.jpg&h=be7ce1cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有好多狗車泊果到架 而且佢地係果到泊車係唔洗比錢嘅 <br />\nps.佢地嘅車個車頭玻璃有識別書 呢樣野係有個曾經嘅死黑警朋友同我講<br />\n條撚樣都係住馬鞍山 架車就係泊果到 <br />\n點解話佢死黑警?因為佢到依家都仲係講緊唔會放過暴徒 <br />\n同叫市民記住自己做過d咩野，後果自負 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以我睇唔過眼了<br />\n提提大家唔好去打爆啊蛇D車 停車場係私人地方 不過大家今日返唔到工可以去散下步 <br />\n順便幫d車打下卡 同埋記得話比馬鞍山街坊知佢地有得免費泊車咁開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9659a912ad14f2c42a6cfc2913d8dc65bcf7089b","tid":1411703,"uid":238378,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T04:21:43.000Z","msg":"我冇野講"},{"pid":"22574c81f128c6aeebbb48810dab89012df1a54a","tid":1411703,"uid":238378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T04:21:57.000Z","msg":"我冇野講"},{"pid":"ba101641dace7fb0212f247cb5ec2fa731bef071","tid":1411703,"uid":238378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T04:22:10.000Z","msg":"我冇野講"},{"pid":"e629a99f8a82b02bc2b850d4e89de132865df42e","tid":1411703,"uid":238378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-