color: red;\">先至</span>唔再相信一國兩制同基本法<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">重點係，中共破壞中英聯合聲明、基本法、一國兩制在先!!!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n中英聯合聲明失效，即係<span style=\"color: red;\">香港主權懸空</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">要求國際社會（尤其美國同英國）同香港人一齊重新討論和解決香港的主權問題</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><br />\n香港自治!<br />\n五大訴求!<br />\n真雙普選!</strong></span>"},{"pid":"3161776a5e51467500f3dd7f800d8ba5a5c8ed14","tid":1411703,"uid":203315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T05:20:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2d01501ac8db9425095d381952af1591636895a7","tid":1411703,"uid":127073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T05:21:11.000Z","msg":"快撚啲打爆哂佢"},{"pid":"af173897fac121a5a9f69b61bf9fe44feefec259","tid":1411703,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T05:22:53.000Z","msg":"識別書係點樣"},{"pid":"a33dae3d73becd207123180ea6f6938314110f2f","tid":1411703,"uid":189591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T05:23:19.000Z","msg":"推推推推推推"},{"pid":"a01b5259b37f65e6d88aafde9fc5070149193bc4","tid":1411703,"uid":89898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T05:23:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42fe0f776da33ef48ea1469c5e6a108117ed539e","tid":1411703,"uid":199257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T05:24:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6829aa83028ec16d8ab4c73e0d786a78b0d5fc3","tid":1411703,"uid":18936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T05:25:20.000Z","msg":"推推先<br />\n呀蛇近排打暴徒咁忙 <br />\n一定無時間洗車<br />\n大家幫幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src